description: Organic Denmark (Økologisk Landsforening) is the premier organic food cluster in the country. Its members include organic farmers, food companies with organic products, and consumers across Denmark. With over 190 member companies, Organic Denmark represents virtually the entire organic food industry in the nation, promoting sustainability, advocating for organic standards, and supporting the growth and development of organic practices and products throughout Denmark, ensuring high quality and trust.
name: Økologisk Landsforening
